casebody.data:
In re J&E DISTRIBUTORS, INC. No. 50P08. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 6, 2008. Jason T. Strickland, New Bern, for J&E, Phillips & June. Kathleen Barry, Assistant Attorney General, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 5th day of February 2008 by Respondents (J.&E., Phillips & June) for Temporary Stay:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference this the 6th day of February 2008."
